  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is for the modeling of impaired judgement in cocaine abusers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to investigate recognition memory and appreciation of changing
      contingencies in relation to a response judgement.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
